    <section>
      <h2>How They Actually Differ</h2>

      <h3>Workflow</h3>
      <p><strong>Jobsolv:</strong> Browse specialized remote/hybrid job board, get AI-matched jobs, review tailored resume for each position, approve and apply—all in one platform. Integrated application process.</p>
      <p><strong>We Work Remotely:</strong> Browse remote job listings, click to view details, apply through external company sites. Traditional job board experience with external applications only.</p>

      <h3>Automation vs Manual Effort</h3>
      <p><strong>Jobsolv:</strong> AI tailors resumes automatically for each job. You review each one (30-60 seconds) before applying. Job matching happens automatically based on your profile.</p>
      <p><strong>We Work Remotely:</strong> Requires manual job browsing and searching. No automatic resume tailoring. You must customize applications yourself or use the same resume for all. All applications go through external company sites.</p>

      <h3>Output Quality</h3>
      <p><strong>Jobsolv:</strong> Each resume is tailored to match specific job requirements with ATS optimization. Higher interview rates because applications are precisely targeted.</p>
      <p><strong>We Work Remotely:</strong> Uses your uploaded resume for all applications. No per-job customization unless you manually edit. Quality depends on your resume optimization skills.</p>

      <h3>Learning Curve</h3>
      <p><strong>Jobsolv:</strong> Simple setup—create profile, upload resume, start browsing. The platform guides you through tailoring and applications.</p>
      <p><strong>We Work Remotely:</strong> Straightforward job board interface. Requires learning effective search strategies and resume optimization. Similar to traditional job boards.</p>

      <h3>Friction Points</h3>
      <p><strong>Jobsolv:</strong> Requires reviewing each tailored resume (adds 30-60 seconds per application). Free tier has credit limits for premium features.</p>
      <p><strong>We Work Remotely:</strong> No automatic resume tailoring. Requires manual job searching and application customization. All applications redirect to external company sites. No integrated tracking or resume tools.</p>
