      <h2>Why Jobsolv Wins</h2>

      <h3>1. Per-Job Resume Tailoring</h3>
      <p>We Work Remotely is a listing board only—no resume tailoring. Jobsolv customizes your resume for every job, matching keywords and skills from each job description. This significantly improves ATS pass rates and interview conversion.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Generic applications get rejected → <strong>Outcome:</strong> Higher interview rates with targeted applications</p>

      <h3>2. Integrated Application Platform</h3>
      <p>Job board, resume builder, tailoring, and tracking in one place. We Work Remotely is a job board only—you still need separate tools for resume optimization, tailoring, and application tracking.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Managing multiple disconnected tools → <strong>Outcome:</strong> One platform for browsing, tailoring, and applying</p>

      <h3>3. AI-Powered Job Matching</h3>
      <p>Jobs come to you based on your profile. No manual searching required. We Work Remotely requires manual job browsing and searching, which takes time.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Spending hours searching job boards → <strong>Outcome:</strong> Relevant jobs matched automatically</p>

      <h3>4. Built-in Resume Builder and Tracker</h3>
      <p>Create and optimize resumes, then track all applications in one platform. We Work Remotely offers job listings only—no resume tools or tracking.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Using separate tools for resumes and tracking → <strong>Outcome:</strong> Complete job search workflow in one place</p>

      <h3>5. Less Competition</h3>
      <p>We Work Remotely has over 34,000 listings and attracts millions of users. Jobsolv's specialized remote/hybrid focus means less competition per job. You're not competing against We Work Remotely's entire user base.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Getting lost among hundreds of applicants → <strong>Outcome:</strong> Better visibility in less crowded marketplace</p>
